                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-4-defend65 t18220911-4-punish18"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 21.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Richardson.</p>
